OL,5, The boss of British Gas owner Centrica 
OL,6, has said he is horrified that debt     
OL,7, collectors have broken into customers' 
OL,8, homes to fit prepayment energy meters. 
OL,10,FThe Times found debt agents working for
OL,11,FBritish Gas expressed excitement at    
OL,12,Fputting these meters in the homes of   
OL,13,Fvulnerable people behind on bills.     
OL,15,F"This happened when people were acting 
OL,16,Fon behalf of British Gas. There is     
OL,17,Fnothing that can be said to excuse it,"
OL,18,FChris O'Shea told the BBC.             
OL,20,FThe firm will stop such installations. 
